            Tags = """["planning","reference"]""",
            ContentJson = """{"title":"Planning Cycles Field Reference","groups":[{"heading":"Cycle Form Fields (Create/Edit Window)","items":[{"label":"Name (required)","value":"Names the cycle, up to 100 characters. Examples: 'Sprint 12', 'Week of Mar 11', 'Q1 Final Push'. Can't be left blank."},{"label":"Start Date (required)","value":"When the cycle begins. New cycles default to today. Must be a real date."},{"label":"End Date (required)","value":"When the cycle ends. New cycles default to two weeks after the start date, and it must fall after the start date."},{"label":"Goals","value":"Optional. A few sentences on what the team wants to get done this cycle. Shows on the cycle board when filled in."}]},{"heading":"Cycle Entry Fields","items":[{"label":"Job Number","value":"The added job's number (for example, 'J-1055'). Shown in bold on each row."},{"label":"Job Title","value":"The added job's title, shown next to its number."},{"label":"Stage","value":"The job's current stage, shown as a colored label."},{"label":"Priority","value":"The job's priority (Urgent, High, Normal, or Low), shown in color."},{"label":"Assignee","value":"Who the job is assigned to. On the cycle board it shows the person's name; in the backlog it shows their initials."},{"label":"Sort Order","value":"The order jobs appear in on the cycle board. Drag a job by the handle on its left to move it up or down."},{"label":"Added On","value":"The moment the job was added to the cycle. Recorded behind the scenes; you won't see it on screen."},{"label":"Completed On","value":"The moment the job was marked done. Completed jobs show a filled check circle instead of an empty one."},{"label":"Rolled Over","value":"Marks a job that carried over from an earlier cycle's unfinished work. Shown with a small replay icon."}]},{"heading":"Cycle Statuses","items":[{"label":"Planning","value":"The status every new cycle starts in. You can freely add, remove, reorder, and complete jobs. See the Activate row below for why the Activate button doesn't show up yet — a known issue you can work around."},{"label":"Active (blue label)","value":"The cycle is underway. The header shows a days-remaining countdown. You can still add or remove jobs, and the Complete and Complete & Roll Over buttons are available."},{"label":"Completed (green label)","value":"The cycle is finished. Every job is locked in its final state and can't be changed. It becomes a record of what was planned and done."}]},{"heading":"Split Panel Layout","items":[{"label":"Left Panel — Backlog","value":"Lists every backlog job not yet added to the cycle you're on. Narrow it by searching (job number or title) or picking a priority. Jobs leave the list when added and come back when removed."},{"label":"Right Panel — Cycle Board","value":"Shows the full cycle: its name, dates, days remaining, done count, and status label up top, then a progress bar, goals, and the list of added jobs. It's also where you drop jobs dragged from the backlog."},{"label":"Drag-and-Drop","value":"Drag a job card from the backlog on the left and drop it anywhere on the cycle on the right to add it. Inside the cycle, drag jobs by their handle to reorder them."}]},{"heading":"Cycle Selector and Header","items":[{"label":"Cycle Menu","value":"The menu at the top of the page. It lists every cycle with its status in parentheses — for example, 'Sprint 12 (Active)'. Pick one to load its details on the right."},{"label":"New Cycle Button","value":"The main button at the top of the page. Opens the new-cycle window with the start date set to today and the end date two weeks out."}]},{"heading":"Buttons and Actions","items":[{"label":"Plus (add) on a backlog job","value":"The button on the right of each backlog card. Adds that job to the cycle right away, no dragging needed. It only shows when a cycle is selected. Hover text: 'Commit to cycle'."},{"label":"Edit (pencil)","value":"The pencil in the cycle's actions. Opens the cycle window already filled in with the current name, dates, and goals so you can change them. Hover text: 'Edit cycle'."},{"label":"Activate (known issue — not showing)","value":"This button is meant to move a cycle from Planning to Active, but a known issue keeps it from showing up right now. You don't need it: a Planning cycle works fully — you can add, reorder, complete jobs, and complete or roll the cycle over without activating. The only thing you miss is the days-remaining countdown."},{"label":"Complete & Roll Over","value":"Shows only while a cycle is Active. Asks you to confirm first. On confirm, it marks the cycle done, starts a fresh cycle the day after this one ends with the same length, and carries every unfinished job into it marked as rolled over."},{"label":"Complete (no roll over)","value":"Shows only while a cycle is Active. Asks you to confirm first. On confirm, it marks the cycle done and sends any unfinished jobs back to the backlog. No new cycle is created."},{"label":"Mark Complete (empty check circle)","value":"The circle on each unfinished job. Click it to mark the job done; the circle fills in. Hover text: 'Mark complete'."},{"label":"Remove (X)","value":"The X on each job. Asks you to confirm, then takes the job off the cycle and returns it to the backlog. Hover text: 'Remove from cycle'."},{"label":"Drag Handle (grip)","value":"The handle on the left of each job. Drag it to reorder jobs within the cycle."},{"label":"Save (window)","value":"The main button in the new-cycle or edit window. Grayed out until the form is filled in correctly or while a save is running. Creates or updates the cycle."},{"label":"Cancel (window)","value":"The second button in the new-cycle or edit window. Closes it without saving."}]},{"heading":"Progress and Stats","items":[{"label":"Done Count","value":"Shown as 'X / Y' at the top of the cycle board (for example, '5 / 12'). X is jobs marked done, Y is jobs in the cycle."},{"label":"Progress Bar","value":"The bar below the header. It fills to match how much is done, with the percentage next to it (for example, '42%')."},{"label":"Days Remaining","value":"Shows only while the cycle is Active. Counts the days from today to the end date, reaching '0' on the last day. It's hidden for Planning and Completed cycles."},{"label":"Backlog Count","value":"Shown at the top of the backlog as 'N jobs'. It's the number left after hiding added jobs and applying your search and priority filters."}]},{"heading":"What the Form Checks","items":[{"label":"Name","value":"Required. Up to 100 characters. Can't be blank."},{"label":"Start Date","value":"Required. Must be a real date."},{"label":"End Date","value":"Required, a real date, and it has to fall after the start date."},{"label":"Goals","value":"Optional. A few paragraphs at most. No set format."},{"label":"Cycle Length","value":"Worked out for you from the start and end dates. When you roll a cycle over, the next one keeps the same length."},{"label":"Save button hint","value":"When the form isn't ready, resting on the Save button shows a note listing what still needs attention (Name, Start Date, End Date)."}]},{"heading":"Who Can Do What","items":[{"label":"View (open the page, read cycles, backlog, and progress)","value":"Open to Admins, Managers, PMs, Engineers, and Production Workers. The whole team can open the page and follow the plan."},{"label":"Create a cycle","value":"Managers and Admins only. Anyone else who tries is turned away."},{"label":"Edit a cycle (name, dates, goals)","value":"Managers and Admins only."},{"label":"Activate a cycle","value":"Managers and Admins only. (The button for this isn't showing right now — see the Activate row.)"},{"label":"Complete or roll over a cycle","value":"Managers and Admins only."},{"label":"Add a job to the cycle","value":"Managers and Admins only. The plus button and drag-to-add both count, so anyone else is turned away."},{"label":"Remove a job from the cycle","value":"Managers and Admins only."},{"label":"Reorder jobs","value":"Managers and Admins only."},{"label":"Mark a job complete","value":"Managers and Admins only."},{"label":"When planning is turned off","value":"Planning has to be turned on for your site. When it's off, the planning area is hidden for everyone, whatever their role."}]},{"heading":"Empty States","items":[{"label":"No cycle selected","value":"The right side shows a note reading 'No cycle selected' with a 'Create first cycle' button."},{"label":"No jobs added","value":"The cycle's job area shows a note reading 'No jobs committed'."},{"label":"No available jobs in backlog","value":"The backlog shows a note reading 'No available jobs'."}]}]}"""
